# === Internal documentation (kept local, not published) ===
# Decision 2026-06-15: Documentation is private knowledge.
# Only the GitHub community MDs and docs/wiki/ (synced to public GitHub Wiki)
# remain tracked. All other MDs stay local only.
#
# Whitelisted (still tracked):
#   - CLAUDE.md, README.md, README.de.md, SECURITY.md, CODE_OF_CONDUCT.md, CONTRIBUTING.md
#   - .github/**/*.md (issue/PR templates)
#   - docs/wiki/** (synced to GitHub Wiki via wiki-sync.yml)
#   - docs/CHANGELOG.md, docs/RELEASE_NOTES.md (generated by release workflow)
#   - violet_poolcontroller_api/{README,CHANGELOG,SECURITY,CODE_OF_CONDUCT}.md (PyPI package)

# Root-level internal docs
/WIKI.md
/CONTROL_IMPLEMENTATION_ROADMAP.md

# All standalone guides & references in docs/ (wiki/, CHANGELOG.md, RELEASE_NOTES.md stay tracked)
/docs/*.md
/docs/help/
/docs/public/
# Whitelist these files
!/docs/CHANGELOG.md
!/docs/RELEASE_NOTES.md

# Dashboard & blueprint internal docs
/Dashboard/*.md
/blueprints/README.md
/blueprints/automation/README.md

# Devcontainer internal doc
/.devcontainer/README.md

# Test artifacts / internal test docs
/tests/docker/*.md

# API package internal docs (PyPI README/CHANGELOG/SECURITY/CODE_OF_CONDUCT stay tracked)
/violet_poolcontroller_api/AGENTS.md
/violet_poolcontroller_api/RELEASE_NOTES_*.md
/violet_poolcontroller_api/docs/
